longBusinessSummary: Matrix Concepts Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in the property development, construction, education, and hospitality business. It develops residential and commercial, and infrastructure projects; and operates private and international schools. The company provides healthcare and hotel management services, as well as clubhouse operator services. Matrix Concepts Holdings Berhad was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Seremban, Malaysia.
